347
00:20:24,454 --> 00:20:25,754
When I took it up with them,

348
00:20:26,424 --> 00:20:27,954
- Mom! - they said it was for...

349
00:20:27,954 --> 00:20:29,863
the next on-site restaurant expected to open two years later.

350
00:20:30,063 --> 00:20:31,363
