351
00:20:31,363 --> 00:20:32,464
What do we do now?

352
00:20:32,464 --> 00:20:33,894
It was a scam.

353
00:20:33,964 --> 00:20:35,234
(Violent Crimes Unit 2)

354
00:20:35,234 --> 00:20:37,504
